------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ 23, 2001 AFTER--------------------------- A BACKGROUND REPORT----, A PANEL DISCUSSES----------- THE DEMOCRATIC REPUBLIC OF THE CONGO FOLLOWING THE ASSASSINATION OF----------- ITS LEADER, LAURENT KABILA.------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------ CRISIS---------------------------------------------- IN CENTRAL AFRICA IND